fields.title: Messages through the website contact page
fields.description: By enabling this notification, you will receive e-mails when a user contacts the website owner through the contact page.

fields.title: A new user has registered
fields.description: By enabling this notification, you will receive e-mails when a new user has registered to the website.

fields.title: A user has activated his/her account
fields.description: By enabling this notification, you will receive e-mails when a user has activated their account on the website and are now able to login.

fields.title: A charge has been created or updated
fields.description: By enabling this notification, you will receive e-mails when a charge has been created or a refund on a previously given charge given.

fields.title: A credit card on file has been updated
fields.description: By enabling this notification, you will receive e-mails when a credit card on file has been updated.

fields.title: A order has been placed
fields.description: By enabling this notification, you will receive e-mails when an order has been placed. It is sent regardless of the charge being successful or not.

fields.title: A billing profile has been updated
fields.description: By enabling this notification, you will receive e-mails when fields such as name, address, etc. have been updated.

fields.title: A subscription is about to expires
fields.description: By enabling this notification, you will receive e-mails when a subscription is about to expire.
